OL,3,CReform councillor under fire after
OL,4,Cvoicemail message branded racist
OL,6,FA newly-recruited Reform councillor is
OL,7,Funder fire for comments made about the
OL,8,FPakistani community in a voicemail
OL,9,Fleft to a journalist.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday 18 June, Councillor
OL,12,FAndrew Barry, who is a Reform
OL,13,Fcouncillor for Merthyr Tydfil Council,
OL,14,Fleft a voicemail seemingly in error to
OL,15,Fan ITV Wales journalist.
