OL,3,CReform councillor under fire after
OL,4,Cvoicemail message branded racist
OL,6,FMerthyr Tydfil Council says a formal
OL,7,Finvestigation process will now begin
OL,8,Fafter it was made aware of the remarks.
OL,10,FJudge Ray Singh CBE, Chair of Race
OL,11,FCouncil Cymru, has called the comments
OL,12,F"offensive", while a statement from
OL,13,Fhis organisation said: "Racially
OL,14,Fcharged language has no place in
OL,15,Fmodern public discourse".
OL,17,FDawn Bowden, Member of the Senedd for
OL,18,FMerthyr Tydfil and Rhymney, has called
OL,19,Fthe remarks "absolutely racist" and
OL,20,F"shocking."
