OL,6,FA Reform UK spokesman said: "The
OL,7,Fprivate conversation involving
OL,8,FCouncillor Andrew Barry has been taken
OL,9,Fout of context, with the recording
OL,10,Fonly picking up snippets of the
OL,11,Fdiscussion.
OL,13,F"They were discussing the failure of
OL,14,Fmulticulturalism and recent warnings
OL,15,Fabout the India-Pakistan conflict
OL,16,Fspilling onto British streets. Past
OL,17,Friots in cities like Leicester and
OL,18,FBirmingham show these are serious and
OL,19,Flegitimate concerns.
